    "name": "Among Us 3D",
    "steam_appid": 3168600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Among Us 3D</i>是一款以团队合作与背叛为主题的派对游戏。召集 4-10 名玩家，一同投入这款备受喜爱的社交推理游戏的完整 3D 版本，开始冒险吧。与其他船员齐心协力，在一个或多个伪装者杀死船上所有人之前完成任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong>Among Us 3D与原版Among Us游戏不兼容，且不支持与原版跨平台联机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/a69919dd5f7dbe19c1e43abceb1618b3.poster.avif?t=1766172560\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/a69919dd5f7dbe19c1e43abceb1618b3.webm?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/a69919dd5f7dbe19c1e43abceb1618b3.mp4?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验早已知晓并热爱的 Among Us核心玩法，如完成任务、破坏设施、召开紧急会议、潜入通风管道——现在以 3D 方式全新呈现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以扮演船员或伪装者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>——船员使命：</strong>完成所有任务，或找出并驱逐伪装者。你要眼观六路，耳听八方——危险可能就在身边潜伏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>——伪装者使命：</strong>破坏设施并消灭船员！陷害船员、潜入通风管道、编织天衣无缝的谎言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/3a69d1d20460ca8063fc48f3d5a9c91a.poster.avif?t=1766172560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/3a69d1d20460ca8063fc48f3d5a9c91a.webm?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/3a69d1d20460ca8063fc48f3d5a9c91a.mp4?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尝试「追逐模式」和定期举办的限时活动，感受不同玩法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新模式「感染者」登场！在「追逐模式」中，感染者将与船员对抗。感染者要在船员完成指定任务前，追捕并感染所有船员，壮大自己的阵营！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>限时活动能让游戏体验更加丰富多变。</strong>从实验性的游戏玩法，到独特的造型风格，常规<strong>限时活动</strong>将在全年持续带来新鲜刺激的内容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/9f5fcffe9acd3647a0ca5f733a2743e2.poster.avif?t=1766172560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/9f5fcffe9acd3647a0ca5f733a2743e2.webm?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/9f5fcffe9acd3647a0ca5f733a2743e2.mp4?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验人气任务的回归，结合创新且沉浸式的第一人称操控方式，焕然一新。在尝试全新任务的同时，也别忘了提防潜藏的伪装者！自定义你的游戏玩法、舒适度和安全设置，打造最佳的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过原生的跨平台游玩功能，在游戏大厅与其他平台的数百万其他船员一起联机——包括《Among Us 3D: VR》的玩家！创建自定义大厅，与亲密好友一起畅玩，设置独特且个性化的游戏参数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong>Among Us 3D与原版Among Us游戏不兼容，且不支持与原版跨平台联机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/346858b51d06a1cdcc102d4f1e11b505.poster.avif?t=1766172560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/346858b51d06a1cdcc102d4f1e11b505.webm?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/346858b51d06a1cdcc102d4f1e11b505.mp4?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过无数种颜色、帽子、手套与皮肤组合，自由打造你的专属船员造型。你还可以用 星尘来进一步扩充你的衣橱。购买这种游戏内货币*，解锁更多个性化装饰，让你的风格熠熠生辉！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong>星尘与原版<i>Among Us</i>的货币体系不兼容，且不可与原版<i>Among Us</i>游戏中的货币互相兑换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/00ff799096a90e19135a0bca6096f5c8.poster.avif?t=1766172560\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/00ff799096a90e19135a0bca6096f5c8.webm?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168600/extras/00ff799096a90e19135a0bca6096f5c8.mp4?t=1766172560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你最喜欢的交流方式，与朋友们组队协作或互相背叛：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—— 使用原生近距离语音聊天，自由畅聊。<br>—— 无需再依赖外部聊天应用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—— 不喜欢开口说话？也可以通过直观高效的快速文本聊天保持沟通。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—— 通过全新的手势系统，用动作表达自我。</p>",
